{
  "page": "Peregrine",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <i><b>Peregrine</b></i> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Ship\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ship\">ship</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peregrine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peregrine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <i>Peregrine</i> takes Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> and her party from <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost_Hill\" title=\"Ghost Hill\">Ghost Hill</a> across the <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_of_Dorne\" title=\"Sea of Dorne\">Sea of Dorne</a> to meet <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. The crossing takes a day and a night, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jayne_Ladybright\" title=\"Jayne Ladybright\">Jayne Ladybright</a> becomes seasick. Arianne loses to <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Garibald_Shells\" title=\"Garibald Shells\">Garibald Shells</a> in games of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cyvasse\" title=\"Cyvasse\">cyvasse</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The party disembarks at the <a href=\"/index.php/Weeping_Town\" title=\"Weeping Town\">Weeping Town</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peregrine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_II_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne II</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403160626\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.027 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.049 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 97/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 510/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1880/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 471/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 583/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   39.732      1 -total\n 82.83%   32.911      1 Template:Italic_title\n  7.32%    2.909      1 Template:Warning/twow\n  5.79%    2.302      1 Template:References\n  5.54%    2.199      1 Template:Warning\n  3.84%    1.527      1 Template:Mbox\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:11941-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403160626 and revision id 333165\n -->\n",
